simpleMVC
--
INSTALLATION :
copy the conf/configuration-changeMe.php to conf/configuration.php and change the database credentials
copy the conf/vhost-sample.conf to your vhosts and customize it with your proper domain
restart/reload the config of your apache and  all is going



GENERATOR :
copy the generator/configuration-changeMe.php to generator/configuration.php and change the database credentials
modify the generator/tables.xml to tell the generator what are the tables you want to generate. it presently contain one table called test.
to generate your module simply type : php admingenerator.php <modulename>. This will generate a module called modulename under business. 
to generate and admin module (containing an admin interface) type : php admingenerator.php admin 


